<tmc-service-paragraph><pub id="RM25T0E"><servcat id="_58"><name>Vehicle Interior</name><section id="_029929"><name>SUPPLEMENTAL RESTRAINT SYSTEMS</name><ttl id="_0138307"><name>AIRBAG SYSTEM</name><para id="RM100000000ZOLP" category="C"><dtccode>B1000/31</dtccode><dtcname>Center Airbag Sensor Assembly Malfunction</dtcname><subpara id="RM100000000ZOLP_02" category="03"><name>DESCRIPTION</name><content5><ptxt>The airbag sensor assembly consists of a deceleration sensor, safing sensor, drive circuit, TC and CG terminal circuit, ignition control, etc.</ptxt><ptxt>If the airbag sensor assembly receives signals from the deceleration sensor, it determines whether or not the SRS should be activated.</ptxt><ptxt>DTC B1000/31 is stored when a malfunction is detected in the airbag sensor assembly.</ptxt><table type="dtc-explan-table" pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="4"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="2" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="3" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.77in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Detection Item</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>B1000/31</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Center Airbag Sensor Assembly Malfunction</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>An airbag sensor assembly malfunction.</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><ptxt>Airbag sensor assembly</ptxt></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZOLP_07" category="10"><name>CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT</name><content5><atten3><ptxt>After replacing the airbag sensor assembly, refer to initialization.*</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" term-id-to="003" href="RM1000000010V0P"/><xref term-id-from="003" href="RM10000000136PW"/></mlink></ptxt><ptxt>*: w/ VSC</ptxt></atten3></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZOLP_05" category="01"><name>PROCEDURE</name><testgrp id="RM100000000ZOLP_05_0001" cellposition="1-1"><testtitle>CHECK DTC</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Check for DTCs.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001" href="RM100000000FW7U"/></mlink></ptxt><gts-info category="dtc-read"><title>Body Electrical &gt; SRS Airbag &gt; Trouble Codes</title><gts-exec function-id="50001"><gts-ecu ecu-id="63"/></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">0</app-param><app-param name="category-div">3</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Body Electrical</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">63</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">SRS Airbag</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param name="selected-state">0</app-param></app-communication></gts-info><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>DTC B1000/31 is output</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>DTC B1000/31 and other DTCs are output</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec><atten3><ptxt>If only DTC B1000/31 is output, do not clear the DTCs. Replace the airbag sensor assembly.</ptxt></atten3><atten4><ptxt>If any DTCs other than DTC B1000/31 are also output, troubleshoot those DTCs first.</ptxt></atten4></test1></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="1-1"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="2-1"><actiontitle>REPLACE AIRBAG SENSOR ASSEMBLY</actiontitle><content6><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM10000000111YP"/></mlink></ptxt></content6></action></result><result label="2" cellposition="1-2"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="2-2"><actiontitle>GO TO DIAGNOSTIC TROUBLE CODE CHART</actiontitle><content6><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000ZOLO"/></mlink></ptxt></content6></action></result></results></testgrp></subpara></para></ttl></section></servcat></pub></tmc-service-paragraph>